  <!-- What is SEO Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-4 md:px-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-cyan-900 leading-tight mb-6">
            What is <span class="text-orange-400">SEO?</span>
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
              Search Engine Optimization (SEO) is the practice of optimizing your website to rank higher in search engine results pages (SERPs)
              for relevant keywords. When done correctly, SEO increases your organic (non-paid) visibility, drives qualified traffic,
              and helps potential customers find your business exactly when they're searching for your products or services.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
              SEO encompasses technical optimization, content creation, link building, and user experience improvements. Google and other
              search engines use hundreds of ranking factors to determine which pages deserve to rank at the top. Our comprehensive SEO
              strategies address all these factors systematically to improve your search presence and drive measurable business results.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
              At Codebrand, we combine technical expertise with creative content strategy to deliver sustainable SEO results. We don't use
              shortcuts or black-hat techniques‚Äîour white-hat approach builds long-term search visibility that withstands algorithm updates
              and grows your brand authority over time.
            </p>
          </div>
