          <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Why SEO Matters</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <div>
                <strong>93% of online experiences</strong> start with a search engine
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <div>
                <strong>First page of Google</strong> receives 95% of all search traffic
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <div>
                <strong>SEO leads have a 14.6% close rate</strong> vs. 1.7% for outbound leads
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <div>
