            Unlike paid ads that stop when you stop paying, SEO builds cumulative value. Rankings and traffic
            grow over time, creating a sustainable source of qualified leads for your business.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM4.332 8.027a6.012 6.012 0 011.912-2.706C6.512 5.73 6.974 6 7.5 6A1.5 1.5 0 019 7.5V8a2 2 0 004 0 2 2 0 011.523-1.943A5.977 5.977 0 0116 10c0 .34-.028.675-.083 1H15a2 2 0 00-2 2v.878A2.997 2.997 0 0110 16.236a2.997 2.997 0 01-3-2.358V13a2 2 0 00-2-2H4.083A5.977 5.977 0 014 10c0-.715.145-1.395.332-2.027z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-900 mb-3">Cost-Effective Marketing</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            SEO delivers one of the highest ROIs in digital marketing. You're reaching people actively searching
            for your solutions, making them highly qualified prospects ready to convert.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M2 11a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5a1 1 0 01-1 1H3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-5zM8 7a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v9a1 1 0 01-1 1H9a1 1 0 01-1-1V7zM14 4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v12a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1V4z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-900 mb-3">Brand Credibility</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Ranking high on Google builds trust and authority. Users perceive top-ranking websites as industry
            leaders, boosting your brand reputation and customer confidence.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
  <Whyus />

  <!-- Benefits Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 px-4 md:px-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-cyan-900 mb-4">
          Why Choose <span class="text-orange-400">Codebrand SEO</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Our proven SEO methodology delivers sustainable results that grow your business.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        {benefits.map((benefit) => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100">
            <div class="text-5xl mb-4">{benefit.icon}</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-900 mb-3">{benefit.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">{benefit.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 px-4 md:px-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-900 via-cyan-800 to-cyan-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-6">
        Ready to Rank <span class="text-orange-400">#1 on Google?</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-xl text-cyan-100 mb-10 leading-relaxed px-4">
        Let's analyze your website's SEO performance and create a custom strategy to boost your rankings,
        increase organic traffic, and drive more qualified leads to your business.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
        <Button text="Request Free SEO Audit" href="/contact" />
        <a href="/services" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 md:px-8 py-3 md:py-4 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm text-white font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300 border border-white/30 text-sm md:text-base">
          <span>View All Services</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
          </svg>
